2004-07-11 02:33  (cyberhorse)
---------------------------------
includes/db_adodb.php
- bug, caused by case sensitivity ... by default ADODB returns rows as objects in capitals, and dp was expecting them in lower case. This bug was preventing logging on (although once logged in, user could do things as normal - that's why the bug creeped in to begin with)
- 
- Sorry guys...

