modules/tasks/todo.php
- Now users are able to filter "Task I own" that is different of "My Tasks"; this means that users can check out tasks that they created
- 
- Another interesting feature is for sysadmins; they now are able to "switch" user in the task modules so they can see how another user is performing. Also this sysadmin user is able to go to "My todo" of the selected user. Excellent for everyday user performance monitoring.

