modules/admin/addedituser.php
- There is a bug with the BIRTHDAY date validation on addedituser.php.
- I have increased commenting of validation failure to assist with troubleshooting.
- Basically, the month field can NOT be in MM format for months 01-09, or the
- form submission will fail.

